data.description: Don't miss this adorable 3 bedroom/2bath home located on the golf course in Pleasant Point!!  This home features  a great open floor plan with all stainless appliances, custom backsplash and granite countertops in the kitchen.  There is a separate laundry room and panty along with an attached 2  car garage.  A wood burning fireplace in the family room makes this an ideal gathering spot.
